<br>
It's regarding the epic and PoP.<br>
<br>
As PoP came we got a new haste. Vallon's Quickening and Speed of vallon. Haste that imo was better and more usefull that the speed of shissar that the epic gives. Do this make the epic pointless as in the effect?<br>
<br>
Sure it's free haste. But with VoQ and the 42min base duration the manacost for this haste is no problem. If vallon will give a meele better damage output why use shissar?<br>
<br>
You can argument that the epic has nice stats. But compared to things that drop even before luclin it's not that super.<br>
<br>
So question is, is the time and effeort to get a enchanter epic really worth it?<br>
<br>
An enchanter can MGB VQ and give the raid a better damageoutput than to click every meele with the epic.<br>
<br>
So do the epic really have a purpouse still to fill? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=467053" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/Alkolist/fullsize/sig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=astyd>astyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#330000>(3/24/03 9:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=378.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Thoughts about the epic</span><hr size=1> <br>
Depends on how you look at it.<br>
<br>
VQ requires level 65 and access to Tier 4 planes, maybe Tier 5 for all I know.  More likely would be to be able to make/get a drop of Speed of the Brood.<br>
<br>
In any case, its a nice item.  If your guild is raiding Tier 4 planes, you don't need the epic.  You probably already had it.<br>
