<br>
Glyphed rune words, which exchange for lvl 65 spells, are not that hard to come by, and drop fairly often from Tier 3 mini bosses.<br>
<br>
My epic would be complete, but those blasted Hate and Fear drops keep eluding me.   I haven't seen a single Vampire essence in over 100 dead revenants.   <br>
<br>
There used to be the argument that epic is still great to have if you need to rehaste people in a hurry, and mana is low.<br>
<br>
